\begin_layout Section
Introduction
\begin_inset Note Note
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Research question(s):
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
* the impact of intervention (aggregated peer ratings) on beliefs,
 adoption,
