\begin_layout Standard
Treated farmers were asked to rate maize seed sold by agro-dealers in their area.
 Farmers could rate an agro-dealer only if they had either personally purchased seed from that agro-dealer or knew someone who had,
 allowing them to report perceived seed performance based on direct or indirect experience.
 Enumerators guided farmers through the list of agro-dealers using a tablet-based application displaying names,
 location descriptions,
 and storefront pictures from the agro-dealer census (see Subsection 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
