\begin_layout Standard
We present the treatment effects on outcomes at both the farmer and agro-dealer levels after one agricultural season (midline) and two seasons (endline).
 To address multiple hypothesis testing,
 outcomes are aggregated into indices following 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "anderson2008multiple"
literal "false"

\end_inset

,
 reported at the bottom of the tables.
\begin_inset Foot
